case.name: Shot a Rocket!
case.description: As Brock attempts to safely put away his Rocket Launcher, he accidentally shoots a rocket out in the process, making it go flying.

case.name: Kaboom.
case.description: By sheer misfortune. The stray rocket he shot during his third stage comes back to hit him, destroying his shirt in the process.

case.name: Question: Skilled Weapon/Object
case.description: Brock will eventually ask everyone about what kind of object they are most skilled with, whether it's a weapon, or just an everyday object.
